properties.areaDesc: Grand Marais to Taconite Harbor MN; Grand Portage to Grand Marais MN; Taconite Harbor to Silver Bay Harbor MN; Silver Bay Harbor to Two Harbors MN
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 6 at 12:53AM CST until January 6 at 10:00AM CST by NWS Duluth MN
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 10 to 20 knots with gusts up to 35
knots and waves 1 to 2 feet expected.

* WHERE...Grand Portage to Grand Marais MN, Grand Marais to
Taconite Harbor MN, Taconite Harbor to Silver Bay Harbor MN
and Silver Bay Harbor to Two Harbors MN.

* WHEN...Until 10 AM CST this morning.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 AM CST THIS MORNING
